race.comment: KICKAGOAL KENNY (2) scored at his most recent appearance here. That continued the very strong form this campaign, with two wins from three starts. Can measure up again. SINGULAR (5) did well last start but found one slightly better here. Nicely placed to play a pivotal role. RUSSIAN SUMMER (8) bounced back last start and got the job done by half a length when he came with a powerful finish as favourite at Innisfail. Taking on a better line-up this time but he deserves plenty of thought. MELO MELO KAVA (6) didn't do a bad job when fourth last start at Mackay. That followed a win at the same track the start prior. Finds a suitable race and can run a bold race.
